{"tid":1245574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［團結］修正版：請連登同意，給勇武的支持與配合","createTime":"2019-06-20T11:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T17:52:15.000Z","uid":37504,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"87b2606fd81f628365574a1684e6b882610a20dc","tid":1245574,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"見到胡志偉個po，好多人讚成，為避免呢個氣氛會令勇武擔心又再出現種種問題，無論之後係點<br />\n<br />\n請各位同意以下<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">重點！任何情況，大家唔衝都要幫手屌走/拉走&mdash;&mdash;》<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">左膠人鏈</span></span>《&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕不篤灰<br />\n3. 絕不講鬼<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">絕不向勇武使用暴力達到和平想法</span><br />\n5. 絕不強行拆走勇武裝備/物資<br />\n6. 任何情況先商量，絕不互相指責<br />\n7. 禁止「大局為重論」「比位人入論」<br />\n8. 勇武應先<span style=\"color: red;\">保護自身安全</span>及脫險（幫忙救人）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">團結！不勸！不阻！</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpYnJFp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpYnJFp.png&h=e28d8fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K49uoFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK49uoFv.png&h=00ccb820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8n2WN7j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8n2WN7j.png&h=662676ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申：我發夢夢到，又無份參與，個人不支持抗爭活動，亦不建議市民參與。</span>"},{"pid":"a7c48c3ac2f8fa16519337e7022b701e76c78921","tid":1245574,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9ab81308d109898320686c7d1b891cc76b05aa6","tid":1245574,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f516416439855d8a0ec551a033693dad27472bcf","tid":1245574,"uid":1